# &lt;u2-tooltip&gt; - element
Tooltips

## Features

- [x] hover or focus
- [x] if it has `tabindex="-1"`, it will not disappear when hovered
- [x] position: top, right, bottom, left
- [x] will stay inside the viewport
- [x] event "u2-tooltip-show" when shown

## Usage

```html
<button>
    hover or focus
    <u2-tooltip>now you see me</u2-tooltip>
</button>
```

```css
u2-tooltip {
    pointer-events:auto;
    font-size:max(12px, .7rem);
    --line-height: 1.4em;
    background:#666;
    color:#fff;
    border-radius:.2rem;
}
```

## Install

```html
<link href="../../../tooltip.el@x.x.x/tooltip.min.css" rel=stylesheet>
<script src="../../../tooltip.el@x.x.x/tooltip.min.js" type=module></script>
```

